About
======================

a python script and makefile to generate outage list in csv format from the PDF
or xls files provided by tepco.

WARNING: This program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful, but
WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of MERCHANTABILITY or
FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.


WARNING: DO NOT RUN this makefile frequently!


Files
======================

Makefile: driver file does the followings:

 1. download pdf or xls files if updated
 2. preprocess pdf files and generate txt files (pdf only)
 3. process xls or txt (if pdf) files and generate csv files

electric_outage_area_list.py: process input file and output csv file


HOWTO
=========================

1. make download
2. make


NOTE: you need python, pdftotext in poppler-utils (if pdf) and python-xlrt (if xls).


